notable_quotes: This buyer did have specs on your aircraft. They were looking at a 3.0 million budget but did not make an offer and it was too low.

analysis.summary: This email from May 27, 2011 discusses the sale of Trump's aircraft (B727/6727) for $2.7 million and relays information from Sean about a potential buyer who had a $3 million budget but did not make an offer as it was considered too low.
